00:25:43.800 --> 00:25:44.640
Desafortunadamente,

00:25:46.040 --> 00:25:47.880
nadie puede ser así.

00:25:50.160 --> 00:25:51.000
Hoy

00:25:52.470 --> 00:25:53.760
